\label{thm: planes}
Let $f: \mathbb{Z}_p^d \to \mathbb{C}$ be a complex-valued function. Let $P_f$ denote the set of $cbw(f)$ lines through the origin that contain $support(\hat{f})$. We have the following explicit decomposition of $f$ into $cbw(f)$ many wavelets $f_s$, associated to $f$:

